Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int[][] grid = { {1, 2, 3},
                 {4, 5, 6},
                 {7, 8, 9} };
int sum = 0;
for (int r = 0; r < grid.length; r++) {
    sum += grid[r][r];
}
System.out.println(sum);
```

