Consider the following method:

```java
public static int[] rowSums(int[][] arr) {
    int[] sums = new int[arr.length];
    for (int r = 0; r < arr.length; r++) {
        for (int c = 0; c < arr[0].length; c++) {
            sums[r] += arr[r][c];
        }
    }
    return sums;
}
```

What does `rowSums(new int[][]{ {2, 3}, {4, 5}, {6, 7} })` return?

