Consider the following method:

```java
public static int mystery(int[][] arr) {
    int result = 0;
    for (int r = 0; r < arr.length; r++) {
        int rowSum = 0;
        for (int c = 0; c < arr[0].length; c++) {
            rowSum += arr[r][c];
        }
        if (rowSum > result) {
            result = rowSum;
        }
    }
    return result;
}
```

