Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int[][] grid = { {2, 4, 6},
                 {1, 3, 5},
                 {7, 8, 9} };
int total = 0;

for (int r = 0; r < grid.length; r++)
{
    for (int c = 0; c < grid[0].length; c++)
    {
        if ((r + c) % 2 == 0)
        {
            total += grid[r][c];
        }
        else
        {
            total -= grid[r][c];
        }
    }
}

System.out.println(total);
```
